===========================================================================
 This file describes changes in the recogbase package starting from v 1.0:
===========================================================================

==========================
 Changes from 1.1 -> 1.2:
==========================

  - Added TryFindHomMethod
  - Compile documentation against GAP 4.5.4


==========================
 Changes from 1.0 -> 1.1:
==========================

  - Fixed a bug with too lazy generation of kernel.
  - Add properties IsKnownSimple and IsKnownAlmostSimple.
  - Set InfoLevel(InfoSLP) to 0 to avoid warning.

